info.description: This package contains filters for use with the Insight Toolkit (ITK) for the reconstruction and analysis of ultrasound images. This includes B-mode image generation, scan conversion, strain imaging, and  ultrasound spectroscopy.
info.name: itk-ultrasound
info.summary: Filters for use with the Insight Toolkit (ITK) that may be particularly useful for the reconstruction and analysis of ultrasound images.
